=\"visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:578px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be35e013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uosEWwB4iaKPdBBHJlD4GYRHOytPia6moa4MPQDibjKXtvUvts27RcWa5OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fcnx0rlumfxnq0a2c%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DGGCz8ppkxxDxc8t1%23QTgOp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌做好知识管理，我是如何用AI搭建知识库的</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4OTgxNzM3OQ==&amp;mid=2652582550&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=46e5197b4625c9a7943d0516339c84ad&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/oS8id3InxlMpvUFquB0aAg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/oS8id3InxlMpvUFquB0aAg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文主张知识库的核心价值在于将隐性经验转化为可产品化的数字资产，通过AI驱动的认知迭代，支撑个人商业系统的稳定增长与竞争壁垒建设，而非仅用于检索资料。 author 以自身实务经验提出五大核心模块（价值主张、方法论、实战案例、表达风格、项目复盘）组合成高价值知识库，并展示如何通过AI反向迭代优化方法论及输出，从而实现“输出倒逼输入、复盘迭代、持续进化”的知识库闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌“人们常常低估了五年能有的改变”丨晚点小数据 2025</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3Mjk1OTQ0Ng==&amp;mid=2247531742&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=bcb905ab2d3030f3d52236ea8a601a43&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SxJQ84AqyaWIKurN_AVnUA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SxJQ84AqyaWIKurN_AVnUA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">未来五年（2021–2025）的回顾显示，社会与产业的变革往往在短期内被高估、在长期内才显现深远影响。文章通过多张图表，梳理了互联网巨头、AI、新能源、消费行为及宏观经济的演变：大平台与AI驱动的变革正在放大市场格局、利润分配和用户黏性，同时中国与全球在AI应用、算力生态与用户付费意愿方面呈现不同路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501968473\" data-type=\"other\" width=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"1.3342592592592593\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21bb1f77&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2QHdmZXYwlJUSx3eJRZpM4ch7SjXjRVGCnqeu76smESwGwgQQTfXZF4SDQ7JMvyNOooq6QZqI6hqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌2025年大模型回顾</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/2025/Dec/31/the-year-in-llms/\" target=\"_blank\">https://simonwillison.net/2025/Dec/31/the-year-in-llms/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">西蒙·威利森（Simon Willison）的 AI 年度回顾，过去一年的大事件基本都提及了，总结和评点得非常好，推荐阅读。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501968474\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"889\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"889\" data-ratio=\"1.062992125984252\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=844fd015&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QHdmZXYwlJUSx3eJRZpM4cicSmibHniaYkNx9Vn0vBvJ16xDLY5iafU1pEvLUMl6YYBCmjTvuswC8tag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6cd7e58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoVw3ibDBtUOIklnu30LHYQBArbGTZwnwokZzibw3DIeVlsscsP5PcbC3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fcnx0rlumfxnq0a2c%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DGGCz8ppkxxDxc8t1%23QTgOp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  </h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0