ei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌将设计原则转化为 AI 兼容的风格规则</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://designprompt.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\">https://designprompt.vercel.app/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">汇总并整合了多种设计风格与核心设计原则，强调以清晰的层级、一致性、可读性与用户目标导向为核心，结合从零开始的重构思维、颜色与深度管理、文本与图像处理等实用方法，帮助在不同场景中实现高效、易用且具有辨识度的界面设计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501968476\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"1920\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9de4028a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QHdmZXYwlJUSx3eJRZpM4cAHwrsPHF1gOcmHlViaGZSEFD59cylia5NnQiaEUP6uicpaehJvRjibbEeEA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 48px 8px 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b74e1aca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoloQt5Gibu37EDyzwasmLC9Ld1Z8ia20TCibPO3Vjh9BB9sKKsPwq4k26g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fcnx0rlumfxnq0a2c%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DGGCz8ppkxxDxc8t1%23QTgOp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌将视频瞬间转化为手绘故事</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/RanFeng/clipsketch-ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/RanFeng/clipsketch-ai</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ClipSketch AI 是一个专为视频创作者、社交媒体运营者和二创爱好者设计的全流程生产力工具。它不仅仅是一个视频播放器，更是一个AI 驱动的内容创作工作台。它可以解析 Bilibili 和小红书的视频链接，让你能够帧级精准地标记精彩瞬间。通过集成 Google Gemini 最新的多模态大模型，它能将这些瞬间一键转化为精美的手绘风格故事板，并自动撰写适配社交媒体（如小红书）的爆款文案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501968479\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"font-size: 14px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"2752\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa57fd64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QHdmZXYwlJUSx3eJRZpM4cFf6licaricueEJA1wV95Ot0q17Yl8HILBNibhZHgLjzc9pM8Mprg3eibnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌302.AI：您的AI生产力加速器</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://studio.302.ai/zh\" target=\"_blank\">https://studio.302.ai/zh</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">302 AI Studio 正是为打破这些壁垒而生。我们将 Claude Code 封装在云端沙盒中，配以直观的对话式交互界面，让 Vibe Coding 的体验变得前所未有的简单顺畅。更重要的是，我们为用户赋予了极致的扩展性与掌控权——让创造真正随心所欲。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501968478\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"1920\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1fd0608f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QHdmZXYwlJUSx3eJRZpM4cpd3lIRN4lNmJPyB9NUjnaGn4tSF0uZlHaugHbtBEFsfYbrhhEM81Wg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:48px 8px 0em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8a4b282&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoQrLTibmRJELUQysO80354ouUOACwWDCCr0NXNjicZbicDGqrqvPSHdibicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fcnx0rlumfxnq0a2c%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DGGCz8ppkxxDxc8t1%23QTgOp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌如果你是中层管理者，允许属下员工上班摸鱼吗？</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://x.com/BQnanqiao/status/2009096354002555156?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/BQnanqiao/status/2009096354002555156?s=20</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你是中层管理者，允许属下员工上班摸鱼吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我记得一个摆摊卖炒粉的老板说过一句话：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当城管来了，你就要装作很怕他们，然后迅速躲起来，他们一般就不会来追你，都是睁一只眼闭一只眼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，如果城管来了，你还一副很叼的样子，让他们没面子，人家就是本来不想搞你，也一定要搞你。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，摸鱼可以，但是不要当着领导的面摸鱼。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本期《有意思小周刊》汇总了近期 AI 知识管理、科技趋势回顾、编程入门教程、AI 设计工具等多元内容，以信息聚合为主。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本期《有意思小周刊》汇总了近期 AI 知识管理、科技趋势回顾、编程入门教程、AI 设计工具等多元内容，以信息聚合为主。",
  "summary": "本文是《有意思小周刊》的第 162 期，主要汇总了作者近期阅读和思考的内容，旨在构建个人知识体系并分享给读者。周刊内容涵盖了多篇文章摘要和工具推荐，包括如何用 AI 搭建知识库、对未来五年社会产业变革的回顾与展望、《晚点小数据 2025》、Simon Willison 的 AI 年度回顾等推荐阅读内容。同时，文章还介绍了地铁信息网站 MetroMan、针对零编程基础者的 Vibe Coding 基础教程、以及如何将设计原则转化为 AI 兼容的风格规则等新发现。工具部分则推荐了 AI 驱动的视频手绘故事生成工具 ClipSketch AI 和 AI 生产力加速器 302 AI Studio。最后，文章分享了一则关于中层管理者是否允许员工“摸鱼”的观点。整体来看，周刊内容丰富，但以信息聚合为主，缺乏原创深度分析。",
